Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.08,0:00:07.44,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Hello everyone, welcome to Wednesday's Downtown!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.44,0:00:11.14,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Here we go - our first presenter is this person!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.46,0:00:14.32,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.88,0:00:19.42,Hamada,,0,0,0,,It's Cunning Takeyama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.94,0:00:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,As an entertainer...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.61,0:00:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...what do you think is the thing you need be most careful of?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.58,0:00:30.58,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,The most?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.19,0:00:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Affairs?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.18,0:00:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.56,0:00:35.60,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Pictoral magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If we put those together, any kind of scandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.48,0:00:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an experience from eleven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.28,0:00:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My picture was put in a magazine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.07,0:00:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...and that caused quite a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.04,0:00:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,During those times as soon as you hear about a scandal...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.32,0:00:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,...your mind just goes blank.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.40,0:00:56.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard about my scandal right before a quiz show on NHK.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.34,0:01:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't answer a single question that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.22,0:01:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My emotions were all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:05.28,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I know that feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:08.53,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,When I see an unfamiliar, important-looking guy like a chief manager...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.53,0:01:12.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,...roaming around set, I think to myself "something definiely happened."
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:15.74,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,After this there's definitely going to be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.02,0:01:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And so this is the theory I have brought today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.54,0:01:23.54,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Theory: Even if your manager told you "a scandalous article about you will come out tomorrow,"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.54,0:01:27.94,Hamada,,0,0,0,,...a professional would finish their job for the day without showing any signs of the upcoming issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.60,0:01:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're a professional...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.90,0:01:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...your personal scandal has nothing to do with the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.99,0:01:36.60,Hamada,,0,0,0,,So they should just push through.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.60,0:01:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was informed of a scandal right before coming here...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...I can't just mope around while I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.38,0:01:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But you couldn't answer questions at the quiz show!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I was truly so shocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even now I barely remember anything about the show!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.10,0:02:01.94,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Also:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:31.30,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today we investigate the theory: Even if your manager tells you "a scandalous article will come out about you tomorrow,"...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.30,0:02:36.42,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...a professional would finish their job for the day without showing any signs of the upcoming issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.02,0:02:43.66,Narrator,,0,0,0,,{\clip(61.5,1004,378,1070)}Today's targets: KoroChiki's Nadal, Panther's Ogata, and Yasumura.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.66,0:02:47.24,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today's targets: KoroChiki's Nadal, Panther's Ogata, and Yasumura.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.18,0:02:53.44,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We had them come in for a fake to show to determine who the most useless entertainer is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.60,0:02:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take the lead since you're the eldest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.64,0:02:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'll take the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.92,0:02:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I can lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:02:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,860)}I can lead too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.92,0:03:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I will lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,By all means, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell, man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.04,0:03:13.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,All three started the gig with high energy levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.48,0:03:18.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Today we've prepared the same scandal article for each of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.76,0:03:24.00,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We will tell them one at a time over the course of the gig.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:29.52,Narrator,,0,0,0,,While the staff "get ready," the comedians wait in the green room.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.12,0:03:33.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,First we target this man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.58,0:03:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Manager: We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,870)}It can't be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.36,0:03:41.28,Narrator,,0,0,0,,We escort him to another room to tell him about the article.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.88,0:03:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\clip(30,1004,612,1080)}...around the end of last year, did you go out drinking with some girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...around the end of last year, did you go out drinking with some girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.62,0:03:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,The end of last year?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.03,0:03:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It was right around December...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:04:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually haven't been out drinking with girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\clip(204,984,606,1078)}Well, it's about this, and they've also taken pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's about this, and they've also taken pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.66,0:04:08.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And the picture shown to Nadal is:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:13.08,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Nadal: Accusations of drinking with underage high school girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.08,0:04:16.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,An article with bad implications.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.29,0:04:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1015,960)}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.34,0:04:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1005,955)}What the hell is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1015,955)}Underage?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.80,0:04:36.62,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Yes, the investigation for this theory began months ago in December.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,End of year party... it's been a great year!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:48.82,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At an end-of-year party with close friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.60,0:04:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.22,0:04:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, she is Jitsukata's type of girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:05:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nadal's friend brought her female friend, who brought her friend to the party...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...to set up the female actresses.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:02.40,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.82,0:05:05.78,Matsumoto Talking Over,,0,0,0,,From the girls' perspective this\N party would be such a letdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.52,0:05:11.91,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As soon as they all have a drink, the setup is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.46,0:05:20.11,Narrator,,0,0,0,,By the way, the girl drinking next to Nadal is the "underage" girl for the sake of the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Jitsukata brought them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.07,0:05:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm pretty sure I confirmed with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1230,980)}How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(290,790)}I'm 22.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(610,500)}I just turned 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,150)}TN: Legal drinking age in Japan is 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,20? Are you sure you're not 19?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(620,500)}I'm 20!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.40,0:05:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg of you, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're really toeing the line here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so real.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed - if I get caught with drinking with an underage girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.14,0:05:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I properly asked if she was over 20.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.27,0:05:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.51,0:05:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This is @#$%&*!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.05,0:05:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy's messed up in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.65,0:05:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,This guy is seriously messed up.  He's deranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,People from Shibuya are generally deranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,People from Tokyo are messed in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.16,0:06:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All these deranged people gathered and created this deranged city.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.39,0:06:07.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the reason drugs are spreading through Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I don't like Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.63,0:06:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There are only these psycho guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never met a proper guy here, seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:18.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,For some reason, Nadal's anger was directed at Tokyo in general.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:20.88,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.41,0:06:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew this would happen if I ever did something like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Using my joke like "yabbeezo!" ("that's pretty bad").
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, "he went for the underage girl."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,"He went for the underage girl, yabbeezo."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The way they write this pisses me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I only have these dirty jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I only have jokes they can easily make puns out of.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.32,0:06:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any pop.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He kept saying it wasn't his fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.97,0:06:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,In the article there are accusations of sexual harrassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(965,1065)}I don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.37,0:06:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(965,1065)}I legit don't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.31,0:06:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say any of these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.41,0:06:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,1065)}Is there a chance you said these things?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,870)}No, no - I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.75,0:07:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I might have asked about the last time she got busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.64,0:07:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Marin, you're seriously in danger though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like guys would target you with your vibe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.45,0:07:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Have any guys recently invited you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.49,0:07:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...to have a one-night stand?  When's the last time?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No comment!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Marin-chan, you can whisper - just tell me when you last did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But it wasn't like...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.14,0:07:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,..."when did you do it last?" in a harrassing way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.09,0:07:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It was more like, "when's the last time you did it?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There was more pop to it.  I was saying it as a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:33.74,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,I don't know how the manager isn't laughing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.33,0:07:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,She went for it pretty recently!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.35,0:07:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me ask Yasumura-san for advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.66,0:07:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,870)}No, hold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still very raw information.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So, please keep it a secret from those two, and don't tell your wife either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.46,0:07:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is rough...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.91,0:07:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Please keep it to yourself for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.35,0:07:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't work like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:08:03.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The thing Nadal was most worried about with the article release was:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You know how I have those commercials? What's happening there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.90,0:08:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...for now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.78,0:08:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute...no no no no no no...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,This is awful!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.82,0:08:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap crap crap crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.94,0:08:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A TV commercial that was just recently confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.73,0:08:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the commercial gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.93,0:08:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Judging from the way things are going, it will probably be scrapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,My head hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a stomachache.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Also the gig you are doing right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,...it might get shelved too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.28,0:08:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,But we can't tell other people...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.45,0:08:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...so for now please continue working normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,My commercial...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:56.28,Default Talking Over,,0,0,0,,What is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.70,0:09:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is awful.
