Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.73,0:20:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are all the other comedians being exposed too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.90,0:20:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1050,1070)}We should cover their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.57,0:20:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1020,1060)}If the story is coming out\N anyway I'll take the fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.41,0:20:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1040,1060)}We would all be screwed, \Nthat's not necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.68,0:20:24.14,Narrator,,0,0,0,,After that display of loyalty...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:27.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...we sent Ogata back on set to continue filming for today's gig.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:29.98,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:38.98,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,Such a somber vibe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.67,0:20:45.67,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The green room was like a funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.86,0:20:54.15,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Let's take a look at the shoot where all the stars believe it will be shelved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.15,0:20:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please begin in 5...4...3...2...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:02.92,Hamada Talking Over,,0,0,0,,It's completely different!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.92,0:21:06.56,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Two hours ago they started with so much energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:14.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Everyone's demeanor has calmed so much...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.34,0:21:16.34,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...it's like we're seeing a different show.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:24.58,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Ogata was hit particularly hard with the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're competing to see who can find as many good things about Venus Fort.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.16,0:21:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can walk around freely and we'll share our answers later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.94,0:21:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:38.02,Narrator,,0,0,0,,It looks like tears could stream down his face at any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the worst.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.60,0:21:48.54,Narrator,,0,0,0,,And now...a segment with a forturne teller to see who has the best luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.54,0:21:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,From here forward...what is going to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...in terms of a career change?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.28,0:22:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,860)}Career change?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.81,0:21:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I want to hear about a career change and whatnot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.93,0:22:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, not as a comedian?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.05,0:22:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,860)}Yeah, I want to hear about non-entertainment stuff too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.05,0:22:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\clip(230,1000,535,1080)}Also, my kids...will I stop being able to see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.06,0:22:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, my kids...will I stop being able to see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.16,0:22:14.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,870)}What happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.40,0:22:19.78,Narrator,,0,0,0,,His thoughts are completely consumed by the scandal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.78,0:22:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see anything about me losing job opportunities?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.14,0:22:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,870)}No no no no...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.17,0:22:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I'm talking comedy jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.64,0:22:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.97,0:22:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I work hard, everything will go well?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.04,0:22:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It will.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.71,0:22:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That gave me some energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.58,0:22:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This is going to come true, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.84,0:22:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not energetic at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.70,0:22:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really going to come true?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.22,0:22:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,870)}You're scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.58,0:22:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.32,0:22:43.77,Narrator,,0,0,0,,At this point they have wrapped up filming for the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.32,0:22:47.48,Narrator,,0,0,0,,As the three of them were set to leave the building...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.48,0:22:51.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,...we set up a fake journalist to ambush them.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.86,0:22:55.63,Narrator,,0,0,0,,How will they react?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.26,0:23:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening, excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.35,0:23:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is in regards to the underage drinking accusations.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.12,0:23:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Can these allegations be considered factual?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.48,0:23:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(420,820)}I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So you admit it? We can consider it the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.06,0:23:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(250,820)}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.36,0:23:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean...I didn't know about it...I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.20,0:23:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you feel bad for what you've done?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.66,0:23:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(270,820)}I mean... I...um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.60,0:23:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(250,820)}Yes...um...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.91,0:23:33.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(235,820)}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.97,0:23:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(540,830)}I should have asked them properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.36,0:23:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1180,590)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.31,0:23:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(210,810)}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.41,0:23:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1110,640)}Is it Ogata? Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.71,0:23:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1180,640)}Is it Ogata?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.05,0:23:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(270,730)}It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.82,0:23:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1220,640)}What? Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.90,0:23:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1125,645)}They told me about that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.76,0:23:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?  Yasumura-san, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.06,0:23:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,860)}They told me a girl I had drinks with...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.74,0:23:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My manager told me between segments.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.73,0:23:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(360,886)}They said I sexually harassed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.57,0:24:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1195,810)}They accused me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.37,0:24:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(310,880)}Oh, this is the exact same.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.54,0:24:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You can go, man.  We'll take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.97,0:24:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(745,680)}It happened to me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.12,0:24:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(262,810)}Eh? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.22,0:24:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(225,820)}Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.64,0:24:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1100,890)}Wait a second...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.22,0:24:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1175,890)}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.11,0:24:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(814,640)}It's me...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.78,0:24:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,890)}Wait a minute, what...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.92,0:24:22.16,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Here we step in to reveal the prank.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.52,0:24:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1135,970)}Oh, we got pranked!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.39,0:24:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(725,830)}Thank god, I'm so relieved!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.21,0:24:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad!  This was a lie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.30,0:24:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,870)}That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.06,0:24:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not getting published, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.83,0:24:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh god, that's a relief!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.43,0:24:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was over.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.64,0:24:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of feeling is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.61,0:24:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: Do you know what show this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.88,0:24:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...Dokkiri Grand Prix wouldn't do anything this messed up...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.98,0:24:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(340,710)}No, they wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.85,0:24:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Wednesday Downtown.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.45,0:24:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,880)}That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.39,0:24:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The script said "Other TV Station!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.99,0:24:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,870)}Are you allowed to do this?! I should sue you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.15,0:24:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,870)}Let's sue them!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.56,0:24:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That is so wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.06,0:25:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The script said !@#$
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.23,0:25:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm so relieved...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.43,0:25:07.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously, so relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.59,0:25:10.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I seriously thought I would have to get a divorce.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.40,0:25:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Staff: All's well that ends well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.11,0:25:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But that was a close one.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.41,0:25:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If I was pressured more, I might have gone for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.58,0:25:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1145,545)}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.15,0:25:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(810,630)}You would have gone for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.45,0:25:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(440,550)}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.95,0:25:27.18,Narrator,,0,0,0,,In conclusion, it was good they didn't go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.18,0:25:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That was amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.56,0:25:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,All three of them got down in the dumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.87,0:25:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want any of the viewers at home to be confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.62,0:25:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Those three did nothing wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.39,0:25:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...and this show is seriously messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.90,0:25:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They asked for their age, and didn't do anything bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.26,0:25:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great educational video.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.34,0:25:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Even as a joke, licking the chopsticks...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.70,0:25:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...and doing this with the cup...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.42,0:25:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...that's seriously gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.94,0:25:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you guys do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.85,0:26:04.40,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Every comedian does that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.88,0:26:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.38,0:26:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no reason to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.76,0:26:11.88,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,People who do that all become comedians.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.00,0:26:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.86,0:26:14.40,Hamada,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.40,0:26:17.10,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Hamada-san definitely does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.10,0:26:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Does everyone do the "nipple cheers" as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.71,0:26:23.31,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,That one was invented by Hamada.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.80,0:26:23.31,Hamada,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.31,0:26:26.20,Matsumoto,,0,0,0,,Hamada is the originator.
